Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.11,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,2,,An acceptance ceremony for the living, is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:09.04,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Having lost their means of survival,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,they're seeking to migrate into Ortus.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, they will be granted a peaceful death.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're gonna kill them?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.01,0:00:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.99,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Ulla know about this?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.44,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she doesn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you jump to that conclusion?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Ulla's...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla's alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Her eyes are the eyes of Death."
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Her words are the words of Death."
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.16,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Her body teeming with Death,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,she shall not allow the living to escape."
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.57,0:01:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Idol of Murder shall not allow them to escape."
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am the ruler of man."
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"I use the equinox to smite any \Nwho doth sojourn in my realm."
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.46,0:01:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am the guardian of all that is dead."
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Ortus's dark side.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.06,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody seen, spoken to, or touched by that princess
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will cease to live.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla is the Idol of Murder.
