Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I only heard about it from him right before I came.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And because until last year,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was alive too.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortus, the land of the dead.{land for the dead}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.32,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Outsiders who wish to live here must die.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, children of immigrants are exempt from this rule.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.59,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They grow up as living beings,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but once they turn fifteen, they're made to choose...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,between dying in order to stay here
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and leaving this place alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose to stay
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was my dream to become a mask maker.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through exactly what they did.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no pain or suffering.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.47,0:05:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it came pretty naturally to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you... you're an outsider.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.50,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you've never given any thought \Nto what it means to be alive or dead, have you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.29,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you accidentally getting mixed up in this and dying
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,just isn't right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.76,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.17,0:06:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla's the first girl I ever met.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.03,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We laughed together.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We were friends,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was really fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.76,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't change the fact \Nthat she's the Idol of Murder.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay inside the inn.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.93,0:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she know?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.28,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Ulla know about her powers?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she know that she has the power to kill people?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had it her whole life.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she {\i1\fs54}not{\i0\fs55} know?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.06,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she's had it her whole life, \Nthere's a chance she hasn't realized it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.16,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, everyone around her is dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.13,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they lied to her and told her the dead are actually the living?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.73,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla would definitely believe them, wouldn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.90,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you noticed it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.76,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up thinking the dead \Naround me were actually alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla is me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the person I was until recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.70,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The me who was surrounded \Nby kindness and lies in her village,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.56,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the me who wasn't told anything about who she was,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.82,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the me who was forced into a role, \Noblivious to everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Ulla are not the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your village's lie
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was doomed to fail.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your father hadn't come along,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the village would've fallen into ruin eventually.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ortus's—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}my{\i0\fs55} lie is different.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.89,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, all of the living will die.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If everyone in the world dies,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla's powers will lose their meaning!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.75,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My lie needs but to last until that time comes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla won't have to be hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that time come?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla's alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead around her don't age.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither do you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a really, really long time passes?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Become the last human alive?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla will be the only one to age...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All by herself!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to protect her.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She must not be hurt.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.48,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was assigned to be her teacher in order to deceive her.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.94,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Create a world unbeknownst to her."
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Reverse the roles of the dead and the living."
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Make her eyes meaningless."
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, Lady Ulla.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.09,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kiriko Zubreska.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiiko?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me "Kiriko," please.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.71,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to keep her safe no matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.70,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to protect her with everything I had.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love her.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.76,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kiriko Zubreska, love Ulla Hecmatika.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.01,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a nice girl...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindhearted, considerate,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and she has a really cute smile.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Her laughter is so lovely.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And her eyes
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,are so pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what would {\i1\fs54}you{\i0\fs55} have done?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.06,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had the chance to shelter \Na girl like that from this cruel world,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what would you do?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop yourself from lying?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I might do the same thing you did.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.64,0:11:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,she needs to know the truth!
Comment: 5,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.49,Default,,0,0,5,,We've been waiting for you, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.93,0:11:31.90,Default,,0,0,5,,Um, I'm gonna go talk to Ulla.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,5,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,5,,We'll give you a ride to the castle.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ulla will come to resent you if you tell her!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not resent the person \Nwho freed you from your ignorance?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not regret knowing?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.84,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you not {\i1\fs54}once{\i0\fs55} wished to live forever within the lie those people built for you?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.02,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand \Nthat what you want to do won't help Ulla?{will not be a definite salvation}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for disturbing you this late.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.67,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you a story about you and me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.03,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm half human, half gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.52,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born and raised in a tiny mountain village.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But that village was a village of the dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.68,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was raised with that fact hidden from me,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and until recently,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize the truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And, Ulla,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.15,0:13:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your circumstances and mine are pretty much identical.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out calmly.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The people around you—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the people you thought were alive—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are actually dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.98,0:13:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who were {\i1\fs54}really{\i0\fs55} alive \Nwere the ones in that tower tonight.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.43,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not alive anymore...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because you looked at them.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.09,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the power to kill \Nanyone you look at, talk to, or touch.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.56,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Am I the Idol of Murder?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.89,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To accept the living in this land, your power was necessary.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko's been deceiving you all this while.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But he only did that
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.05,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Is that everything you came to tell me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.90,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was doing this for you,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe I was just doing it for myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.91,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know everything now, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't forgive me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko, we have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceive her.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only thing the elders wish of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}The two of you look so sad right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I don't want that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I love both of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So please,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need Ai to tell me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.73,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You... knew?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.96,0:16:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I only knew half of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.76,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the feeling that my eyes had {\i1\fs54}some{\i0\fs55} effect on people.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.90,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I also knew that all of you were \Ndesperately trying to hide that from me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.75,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know exactly what I was doing, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, why didn't you say something?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't really mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.40,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it was something \Neveryone wanted to keep from me,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mind not knowing.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I understand now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I kill people.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.69,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't fully understand what it means to kill someone in this world.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.28,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them had such a peaceful smile on his face.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And another let out a big sigh of relief.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.19,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There were those who had weapons but stopped fighting to enter Ortus.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}Still others refused to join us \Nand headed for the wastelands instead.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.14,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of them looked like they'd been set free.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Ai...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that death—do you think that {\i1\fs54}I'm{\i0\fs55} evil?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.22,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.04,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on a journey to find that out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.01,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, you and I are really similar.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not exactly the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.44,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like a bird in the sky that refuses to be caged.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.84,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this cage called Ortus.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.05,0:18:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of which, this cage is home to Kiriko.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the time or place,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he's always protecting me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ulla.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I love the person I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.14,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}But there are two things that sadden me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}One of them is being unable to see you, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}And the other is being unable to hold you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.07,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my treasured friend, and yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}So...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.96,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Come on.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.90,0:20:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are dazzling.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}There's someone I'd like you to meet.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I say this?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.54,0:20:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After you ran off, Scar suddenly showed up.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Celica Hecmatika,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla's elder sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been asleep all this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.72,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla's mother hated every single thing around her...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She hated the way the world had changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.24,0:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She hated the nomadic life \Nshe had to live after she got married.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She hated her dead husband.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what she hated the most...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,were the twins still in her womb.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.87,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Driven to the brink of death by the delivery,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,she went insane and made an incredibly powerful wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:27.30,Nichiyoubi,,0,0,50,,{\an8\blur0.6\fscx44\fscy44}Die, humans.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.78,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulla innocently accepted that desire,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.67,0:21:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but Celica rejected it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.05,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been you this whole time, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.90,0:22:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who's been calling out to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.73,0:22:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I always felt
Dialogue: 5,0:22:17.39,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that my sister had frozen her time—\Nwaiting for something.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Now I know what it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my daughter.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.04,0:22:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,please take care of my sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.67,0:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai Astin, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.74,0:23:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined there'd be someone else \Nliving the same dream as me.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This world really is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:35.81,nextep,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,900)\blur0.6}Next Episode
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.61,0:23:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,School?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.24,Default,,0,200,0,,Goran Academy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.84,0:23:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...you have been accepted{\alpha&HFF&}...{\alpha&H00&} \Ninto this academy.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.94,0:23:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were sold out, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.97,0:23:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because my little ghost here \Nplayed a prank on us.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.47,0:23:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, nice to meet you...{students of Goran Academy.}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:40.29,0:23:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you all doing?!
